Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.70,0:01:31.32,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}奇跡は現実のとなりにある　必ずある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.06,0:01:42.51,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}小さなため息　心配だから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.81,0:01:48.40,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}うしろ姿　見守ってるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:54.34,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}違いだから　こんなこと言わないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:02:01.98,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}きっと人は　一人じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:08.30,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}たとえば　そっと指先に触れる思い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:12.67,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}たとえば　大切な時を忘れ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:20.04,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}だからも　もっと少し高く上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:25.76,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}見てるよ　あの子の瞳に映るヒカリ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:31.92,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}エナジーは世界を全部満ちる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:39.92,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}今だけは　力を貸してあげるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.70,0:01:31.32,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}奇迹 总是在现实的身旁出现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.06,0:01:42.51,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}轻轻地叹息 那是因为心中的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.81,0:01:48.40,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}现在 守望着你的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:54.34,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}不对 我不会说出那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:02:01.98,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}人 不是孤单的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:08.30,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}那怕是 轻轻地触碰那指尖的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:12.67,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}那怕是 忘却贵重的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:20.04,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}所以 想要到更高地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:25.76,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}看吧 那孩子眼中的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:31.92,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}让全世界充满了能量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:39.92,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}只有现在 能将力量借于你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.17,0:00:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让大家担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鄙人 普拉格·克莱欧斯塔斯塔特 今日回归二科
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 普拉格
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.94,0:00:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是可以的话 倒是不希望你回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.17,0:00:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好过分了 难得人家干劲十足的说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.80,0:00:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手臂 已经痊愈了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 对工作不会有任何影...啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.37,0:00:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟...哟 好久不见 那之后就没来过医院呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.66,0:00:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还...还在生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛痛痛痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么啊 搞突袭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.31,0:00:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为你那双伤残的手能工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你难道 还没有康复
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离双臂的重建还有两周
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这么短的时间内 不可能康复
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 因为那个...想快回工作...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.21,0:01:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想回来...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.82,0:01:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大笨蛋...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 目前的状态还不能胜任工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:02:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜她又会胡乱做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就从主治医生那儿了解了情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.79,0:03:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛 好痛 好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都惨叫成这样了 还想隐瞒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好痛 好痛 好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.85,0:03:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做科室工作吗 报告者或是输入资料什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.57,0:03:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手指还不能运动自如
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我现在就回医院去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要不要不要不要 绝对不要——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是孩子 只是让你不要吵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为亚蕾丝塔老做多余的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那都是因为你干傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.22,0:03:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}巴蕾斯科长 今天完工后 要召开紧急会议
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急会议？等会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都快给老娘闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CHARGE08 胡来和温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.46,0:04:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科长也好天真啊 说什么“在现场做康复训练”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是所谓的“现场主义”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 接下来要开始工作 我和你分头干
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的任务是找到好的充电对象 进行锁定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把位置转发给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做这些就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.40,0:04:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 充电呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么都没用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这任务很适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:04:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么嘛 你这只冷血女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆乳女 侧漏女 爱哭女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你说你那双手能干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连充电道具也拿不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.57,0:05:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 唉 还有什么好说的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 没话说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不听我的指示 就不止这点程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有植入基本动作的辅助信号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在维持上 会显得更轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,效率也应该提高了 感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还有点疼痛感 但已经好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 我复职打打下手什么的...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说傻话！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是到能过正常生活的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因人而异也要花费半年以上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说重建成功了 但手臂组织毕竟是新的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没完全适应
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 绝对不能着急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了吗 对你这种患者而言 胡乱的操作...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 胡乱的操作会适得其反...吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想乱来 只是...想快点重返工作嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去问下下吧 今天应该没课...呼呼呼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪~登君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧 闪~登君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪~登君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪~登君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有种就来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊...圣利奈的奶子...不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.86,0:07:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧 那家伙变飞机场了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪了呢 闪登君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法 这里就暂时...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 齐心协力 打倒它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚买东西回来...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪登君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不打声招呼 就闯入我家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙的出场 久违了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管如此我还是努力地让那“Z体质”的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恢复了精神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我要去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何今天终于 临时复职了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.21,0:09:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等得我好苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在想“那家伙是笨蛋”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来他家 或许是我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪登君？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普拉格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我坐的这张床 能碰到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把衣服脱了到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋...你在误会什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样 发展太快了吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 只脱外套就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你们的世界 康复技术看来也和我们这边差不多嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按摩的话就说按摩嘛 不一定要在床上...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:20.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我坐在这里你才能碰得到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了啦 我又没在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人 明明手掌出汗黏糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是...是因为能闪登君的手太热了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生说“温暖的才更有效果”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼痛止住了 手臂能抬起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢啦 我超开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后不要乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.53,0:11:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪登君 和平时有点不大一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有点 透不过气来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}喂 看那个 那个啊那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}看那个 喂 听到了吗喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我按摩 关心我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.74,0:11:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我受伤 才对我那么温柔的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要发呆到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个中学生 很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可疑？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个 不是需要充电的对像么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要一起吃么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:09.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充电
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也进展顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息下也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 似乎是在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.74,0:12:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 也不是想去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.77,0:12:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 我也不是期待着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪登
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎喵来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚蕾丝塔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人独吞闪登
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很早就想这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的是亚蕾丝塔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然平常不能像这样坦诚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这才是真的 我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.87,0:13:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啾~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪登 是不是还在外面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是对象
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是闪登君真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光看着就知道是不是对象
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.65,0:13:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和亚蕾丝塔比赛的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锻炼过了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 警戒深度是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪登君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在了X2
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,bingo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 马上就充电呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要给亚蕾丝塔传送位置情报
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我双手不能用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对象找到了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后的充电就由亚蕾丝塔...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.11,0:14:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就是这么决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀 还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让别人来做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 的确不是什么温柔 闪登君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽是胡来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是胡来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是要做到双手报废了为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时机？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算现在充电了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为也不会有什么效果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时机是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有在心情转好的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和真心想有什么改变的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充电的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自身就会有意识的打破现状
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪登君？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起等待时机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来创造的话 不是更快么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪登君 要干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你其实也喜欢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种波涛汹涌的大姐姐的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逼近过来的话 就受不了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.48,0:16:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真下流 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.71,0:16:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锵锵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.06,0:16:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.19,0:17:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好觉悟了么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你 闪登君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这双手 也抓不起插头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是 算了的好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 一发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充--电！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀 感觉忽然精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充电做到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了 闪登君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...呐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有个悲剧的通告
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.56,0:18:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地线
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又忘记连接了么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新型制服是残次品 这之前听说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这...个...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原型制服是不是...也是残次品...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想见 闪登
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪登君个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普拉格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚蕾丝塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才为止 到底在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情报一次都没有传送过来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只有一个人 但是充电了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那副身体 怎么充电？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是让闪登君来帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 搞什么 那副害羞的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道 被闪登君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充电满满了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是我想见闪登的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙真碍事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 无视了我的命令了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 很让我头疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿嘿 忘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被闪登君做的按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.32,0:20:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.11,0:20:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开 滚开 滚开...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很疼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是老样子 要人照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:21:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕阳下的那只蜻蜓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后是停留在哪只屁股上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.65,0:21:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近江闪登 烦恼的青春第一页
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没...什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这显示了通常充电的电量使用情况
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 这是出现问题的事例
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,异常的电量消耗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个对象就算是被认定为Z
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不能让人认为会产生那么巨大的电量消耗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据负责的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:21:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.62,0:22:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个不能忽视的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于我们来说 这种情况下可能有某种干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您怎么认为 帕鲁斯科长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.31,0:23:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是第一次 所以吓了一大跳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.37,0:24:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪登君 那么大 那么热 稍微硬硬的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.62,0:24:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.20,0:24:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是说的闪登的按摩吧 不要说得那么煽情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.37,0:24:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 比较燃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.26,0:24:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不燃就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.77,0:24:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 一发 充电娘
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 监查室特务部 漏电娘
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.11,0:24:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是敌是友 谜之美女组合登场
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.81,0:24:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故事将越来越有趣了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.28,0:24:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也那么那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.14,0:22:29.45,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}本当はとってもタフなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.51,0:22:32.20,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}ひとり でも平気で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.27,0:22:34.93,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}どこにでも行けるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:37.61,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}恋人なんていらない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.81,0:22:40.57,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}たくましく生きて行くんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.64,0:22:43.13,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}と決めてたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.31,0:22:45.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}君と出会うまでは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.33,0:22:53.15,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}それはありがちな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:22:59.08,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}はなしじゃないかなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.41,0:23:06.75,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}だってね私はいつも特別
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.97,0:23:09.72,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}君にもきっとスペシャルでしょ
